gcode_macro START_PRINT.gcode:
{% set BED_TEMP = params.BED_TEMP|default(60)|float %}
{% set EXTRUDER_TEMP = params.EXTRUDER_TEMP|default(190)|float %}
RED_10 ; set lights to red and 10%
G90 ; set absolute coordinates
M83 ; set extruder to relative
M140 S{BED_TEMP} ; wait for bed temperature
M104 S150 ; start heating extruder to no ooze temp
G4 S10 ; allow partial warmup
G28 ; Home all axes
Z_TILT_ADJUST
G29
;LEVEL_BED_ADVANCED MAX_AGE=10 ; probe mesh eventually
RED_50 ; brighten it up since we're nearing the end
M104 S{EXTRUDER_TEMP} ; start final warm up
G1 Z50 F240
G1 X2 Y10 F3000
M190 S{BED_TEMP} ; wait for bed temp to stabilize
M109 S{EXTRUDER_TEMP} ; wait for nozzle temp to stabilize
WHITE_50 ; set lights to white for printing
G1 Z0.28 F240
G92 E0
G1 Y140 E10 F1500 ; prime the nozzle
G1 X2.3 F5000
G92 E0
G1 Y10 E10 F1200 ; prime the nozzle
G92 E0

gcode_macro start_print.gcode:
{% set BED_TEMP = params.BED_TEMP|default(60)|float %}
{% set EXTRUDER_TEMP = params.EXTRUDER_TEMP|default(190)|float %}
RED_10 ; set lights to red and 10%
G90 ; set absolute coordinates
M83 ; set extruder to relative
M140 S{BED_TEMP} ; wait for bed temperature
M104 S150 ; start heating extruder to no ooze temp
G4 S10 ; allow partial warmup
G28 ; Home all axes
Z_TILT_ADJUST
G29
;LEVEL_BED_ADVANCED MAX_AGE=10 ; probe mesh eventually
RED_50 ; brighten it up since we're nearing the end
M104 S{EXTRUDER_TEMP} ; start final warm up
G1 Z50 F240
G1 X2 Y10 F3000
M190 S{BED_TEMP} ; wait for bed temp to stabilize
M109 S{EXTRUDER_TEMP} ; wait for nozzle temp to stabilize
WHITE_50 ; set lights to white for printing
G1 Z0.28 F240
G92 E0
G1 Y140 E10 F1500 ; prime the nozzle
G1 X2.3 F5000
G92 E0
G1 Y10 E10 F1200 ; prime the nozzle
G92 E0

gcode_macro end_print.gcode:
{% set X_MAX = printer.toolhead.axis_maximum.x|default(200)|float %}
{% set Y_MAX = printer.toolhead.axis_maximum.y|default(200)|float %}
G91
G1 E-2 F2700
G1 E-1.5 Z0.2 F2400
G1 X5 Y5 F6000
G1 Z10
G90
G1 Z{printer.toolhead.position.z + 10} F600
G1 X{X_MAX / 2} Y{Y_MAX} F6000
M106 S0
M104 S0
M140 S0
SAVE_IF_SET     ; SAVE_CONFIG if a mesh was probed in START_PRINT
M84 ; Disable steppers

delayed_gcode welcome_48.gcode: SET_LED LED=printer_lights RED=.3 GREEN=.3 BLUE=.3 TRANSMIT=1

delayed_gcode welcome_40.gcode: SET_LED LED=printer_lights RED=.3 GREEN=0 BLUE=0 TRANSMIT=1
